Subject: WOOO HOOO! Bus Benefit Starts Tomorrow in Grand Rapids, MI -

Hello Fellow Volks Folks,

WOOO HOOO! We are so excited! The eighth Annual "Bus Benefit" hosted by
"Buses By the Beach" in Grand Rapids, MI starts tomorrow! Special thanks go
to our 2010 Gold Level Sponsors; GoWesty www.gowesty.com
<http://www.gowesty.com/>  and River Valley Auto! www.rivervalleyauto.net
<http://www.rivervalleyauto.net/> 

This event is our main fund raiser for The Phoenix Society for Burn
Survivors. We are really looking forward to seeing everyone and it looks
like we are going to have another great turn out again this year of Bus
Pilots from all over the US and Canada! We are not sure if this can be any
kind of indicator but we have pre-sold more t-shirts this year then the last
four years combined! We think it is going to be a huge year!  

 

Campground Information: 

 

If you are coming and would like some campground information we have a post
in our forum. To view the post click on the following link:
